<html>

<head>
	<title>
		Sign Up
	</title>
	<link rel="stylesheet" href="../assets/css/reset.css">
	<link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/5.15.3/css/all.min.css" />
	<link rel="stylesheet" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Roboto:wght@400;500;700&amp;display=swap" />
	<link rel="stylesheet" href="../assets/css/sign-up.css"><!-- Move your css to assets/css -->
	<link rel="stylesheet" href="../componentes/footer-header.css"><!-- Must import this for the head and footer styles -->

	<script src="../assets/js/sign-up.js" defer></script>
	<link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0-alpha1/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">


</head>

<body>
	<%- include('../componentes/header.ejs') %>

<!-- For the header -->
	<div class="container">
		<div class="testimonials">
			<h2>
				Trusted by Language Learners Worldwide – See Their Success Stories
			</h2>
			<p>
				Students from all backgrounds have joined us to improve their language skills. Here’s what they have to
				say about their learning experience.
			</p>
			<div class="testimonial-item active">
				<img alt="Student photo" height="50"
					src="https://storage.googleapis.com/a1aa/image/t85Y3oEhqwqGNJuIe8HT7GDQXzIHyf3sJK1wXKO2mGpWnFmTA.jpg"
					width="50" />
				<div>
					<p>
						I struggled with French for years, but this course really clicked for me. The structured
						approach and helpful instructors made all the difference. Now, I’m having conversations with
						ease. Highly recommend!
					</p>
					<p class="name">Sarah L</p>
				</div>
			</div>
			<div class="testimonial-item">
				<img alt="Student photo" height="50"
					src="https://images.pexels.com/photos/16160880/pexels-photo-16160880/free-photo-of-man-in-t-shirt.jpeg?auto=compress&cs=tinysrgb&w=1260&h=750&dpr=1"
					width="50" />
				<div>
					<p>
						Thanks to this platform, learning Mandarin has been a breeze. The lessons are perfectly paced,
						and I love how quickly I can apply what I’ve learned in everyday conversations. Best learning
						experience!
					</p>
					<p class="name">John D</p>
				</div>
			</div>
			<div class="testimonial-item">
				<img alt="Student photo"
					src="https://images.pexels.com/photos/16160855/pexels-photo-16160855/free-photo-of-smiling-man-in-eyeglasses.jpeg?auto=compress&cs=tinysrgb&w=1260&h=750&dpr=1" />
				<div>
					<p>
						I’ve tried many language platforms, but this is the first one that actually worked for me. The
						German lessons are practical and easy to follow, and I’m already using what I’ve learned in
						real-life situations. Highly recommended!
					</p>
					<p class="name">
						Emily R
					</p>
				</div>
			</div>
			<div class="testimonial-item">
				<img alt="Student photo" height="50"
					src="https://images.pexels.com/photos/16173670/pexels-photo-16173670/free-photo-of-man-in-t-shirt-standing-at-corridor.jpeg?auto=compress&cs=tinysrgb&dpr=1&w=500"
					width="50" />
				<div>
					<p>
						Studying Arabic felt impossible before, but now I’m making real progress. The lessons are so
						well-designed, and the feedback has been incredibly helpful. I can finally read Arabic texts
						with confidence
					</p>
					<p class="name">Michael B</p>
				</div>
			</div>
			<div class="testimonial-item">
				<img alt="Student photo" height="50"
					src="https://images.pexels.com/photos/16105554/pexels-photo-16105554/free-photo-of-smiling-man-against-big-dense-foliage.jpeg?auto=compress&cs=tinysrgb&w=1260&h=750&dpr=1"
					width="50" />
				<div>
					<p>
						This platform made learning Japanese so much easier. The interactive lessons keep me motivated,
						and the support is fantastic.
						I’ve gone from knowing nothing to being able to read and write in just a few months!</p>
					<p class="name">
						Jessica T
					</p>
				</div>
			</div>
			<div class="testimonial-item">
				<img alt="Student photo" height="50"
					src="https://images.pexels.com/photos/16105475/pexels-photo-16105475/free-photo-of-young-smiling-man.jpeg?auto=compress&cs=tinysrgb&w=1260&h=750&dpr=1"
					width="50" />
				<div>
					<p>
						Learning Spanish was overwhelming until I joined this platform. The lessons are clear and
						engaging, and I’ve made more progress than I ever thought possible.
						I can now speak confidently with native speakers. Amazing experience!</p>
					<p class="name">
						David K
					</p>
				</div>
			</div>
			<div class="testimonial-navigation">
				<button onclick="prevTestimonial()">
					<i class="fas fa-arrow-left"></i>
				</button>
				<button onclick="nextTestimonial()">
					<i class="fas fa-arrow-right"></i>
				</button>
			</div>
		</div>
		<div class="signup">
			<h2>
				Sign Up
			</h2>
			<p>
				Create an account to unlock exclusive features.
			</p>
			<% if (error) { %>
				<div id="error-message">
					<p><%= error %></p>
				</div>
			<% } %>
			<form method="POST" action="/api/sign-up/v1">
				<input placeholder="Enter your Name" required type="text" name="name" />
				<input placeholder="Enter your Email" required type="email" name="email" />
				<input placeholder="Enter your Password" required type="password" name="password" />
				<label class="checkbox">
					<input required type="checkbox" />
					I agree with
					<a href="#">Terms of Use</a>and<a href="#">Privacy Policy</a>
				</label>
				<button type="submit">
					Sign Up
				</button>
				<div class="login-link">
					Already have an account?
					<a href="/pages/login-page/log-in.html">
						Login
					</a>
					→
				</div>
			</form>
		</div>
	</div>
	<%- include('../componentes/footer.ejs') %><!-- For the footer -->

</body>

</html>